30 using System;
31 using System.Runtime.InteropServices;
32 using System.Text;
33 using Alis.Core.Aspect.Base.Dll;
34 using Alis.Core.Graphic.Properties;
35 
36 namespace Alis.Core.Graphic.SDL
37 {
41  public static class Sdl
42  {
46  static Sdl()
47  {
48  if (RuntimeInformation.IsOSPlatform(OSPlatform.OSX))
49  {
50  switch (RuntimeInformation.ProcessArchitecture)
51  {
52  case Architecture.Arm64:
53  EmbeddedDllClass.ExtractEmbeddedDlls("sdl2.dylib", NativeGraphic.osx_arm64_sdl2);
54  break;
55  case Architecture.X64:
56  EmbeddedDllClass.ExtractEmbeddedDlls("sdl2.dylib", NativeGraphic.osx_x64_sdl2);
57  break;
58  }
59  }
60 
61  if (RuntimeInformation.IsOSPlatform(OSPlatform.Windows))
62  {
63  switch (RuntimeInformation.ProcessArchitecture)
64  {
65  case Architecture.Arm64:
66  EmbeddedDllClass.ExtractEmbeddedDlls("sdl2.dll", NativeGraphic.win_arm64_sdl2);
67  break;
68  case Architecture.X86:
69  EmbeddedDllClass.ExtractEmbeddedDlls("sdl2.dll", NativeGraphic.win_x86_sdl2);
70  break;
71  case Architecture.X64:
72  EmbeddedDllClass.ExtractEmbeddedDlls("sdl2.dll", NativeGraphic.win_x64_sdl2);
73  break;
74  }
75  }
76 
77  if (RuntimeInformation.IsOSPlatform(OSPlatform.Linux))
78  {
79  switch (RuntimeInformation.ProcessArchitecture)
80  {
81  case Architecture.Arm64:
82  EmbeddedDllClass.ExtractEmbeddedDlls("sdl2.so", NativeGraphic.linux_arm64_sdl2);
83  break;
84  case Architecture.X64:
85  EmbeddedDllClass.ExtractEmbeddedDlls("sdl2.so", NativeGraphic.linux_x64_sdl2);
86  break;
87  }
88  }
89  }

1957  internal static int Utf8Size(string str)
1958  {
1959  if (str == null)
1960  {
1961  return 0;
1962  }
1963 
1964  return str.Length * 4 + 1;
1965  }
1966 
1974  internal static byte[] Utf8Encode(string str, byte[] buffer, int bufferSize)
1975  {
1976  if (str == null)
1977  {
1978  return null;
1979  }
1980 
1981  Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(str, 0, str.Length, buffer, 0);
1982  buffer[str.Length] = 0; // Null-terminate the string
1983 
1984  return buffer;
1985  }
1986 
1987 
1993  internal static byte[] Utf8EncodeHeap(string str)
1994  {
1995  if (str == null)
1996  {
1997  return null;
1998  }
1999 
2000  int bufferSize = Encoding.UTF8.GetByteCount(str) + 1;
2001  byte[] buffer = new byte[bufferSize];
2002  Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(str, 0, str.Length, buffer, 0);
2003  buffer[bufferSize - 1] = 0; // Null-terminate the string
2004 
2005  return buffer;
2006  }
2007 
2008 
2015  public static string UTF8_ToManaged(IntPtr s, bool freePtr = false)
2016  {
2017  if (s == IntPtr.Zero)
2018  {
2019  return null;
2020  }
2021 
2022  byte[] bytes = new byte[0];
2023  int len = 0;
2024  while (Marshal.ReadByte(s, len) != 0)
2025  {
2026  len++;
2027  }
2028 
2029  if (len == 0)
2030  {
2031  return string.Empty;
2032  }
2033 
2034  bytes = new byte[len];
2035  Marshal.Copy(s, bytes, 0, len);
2036  string result = Encoding.UTF8.GetString(bytes);
2037 
2038  if (freePtr)
2039  {
2040  SDL_free(s);
2041  }
2042 
2043  return result;
2044  }

2055  public static uint SDL_FOURCC(byte a, byte b, byte c, byte d) => (uint) (a | (b << 8) | (c << 16) | (d << 24));

3011  [DllImport(NativeLibName, EntryPoint = "SDL_ShowMessageBox", CallingConvention = CallingConvention.Cdecl)]
3012  private static extern int INTERNAL_SDL_ShowMessageBox([In] ref InternalSdlMessageBoxData messageboxdata, out int buttonid);
3013 
3014 
3020  private static IntPtr INTERNAL_AllocUTF8(string str)
3021  {
3022  if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(str))
3023  {
3024  return IntPtr.Zero;
3025  }
3026 
3027  byte[] bytes = Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(str + '\0');
3028  IntPtr mem = SDL_malloc(bytes.Length);
3029  Marshal.Copy(bytes, 0, mem, bytes.Length);
3030  return mem;
3031  }
3032 
3039  public static int SDL_ShowMessageBox(ref SdlMessageBoxData messageboxdata, out int buttonid)
3040  {
3041  InternalSdlMessageBoxData data = new InternalSdlMessageBoxData
3042  {
3043  flags = messageboxdata.flags,
3044  window = messageboxdata.window,
3045  title = INTERNAL_AllocUTF8(messageboxdata.title),
3046  message = INTERNAL_AllocUTF8(messageboxdata.message),
3047  numbuttons = messageboxdata.numbuttons
3048  };
3049 
3050  InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData[] buttons = new InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData[messageboxdata.numbuttons];
3051  IntPtr buttonsPtr = IntPtr.Zero;
3052 
3053  try
3054  {
3055  for (int i = 0; i < messageboxdata.numbuttons; i++)
3056  {
3057  buttons[i] = new InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData
3058  {
3059  flags = messageboxdata.buttons[i].flags,
3060  buttonid = messageboxdata.buttons[i].buttonid,
3061  text = INTERNAL_AllocUTF8(messageboxdata.buttons[i].text)
3062  };
3063  }
3064 
3065  buttonsPtr = Marshal.AllocHGlobal(buttons.Length * Marshal.SizeOf<InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData>());
3066  for (int i = 0; i < buttons.Length; i++)
3067  {
3068  IntPtr buttonPtr = buttonsPtr + i * Marshal.SizeOf<InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData>();
3069  Marshal.StructureToPtr(buttons[i], buttonPtr, false);
3070  }
3071 
3072  data.buttons = buttonsPtr;
3073 
3074  IntPtr colorSchemePtr = IntPtr.Zero;
3075  if (messageboxdata.colorScheme != null)
3076  {
3077  colorSchemePtr = Marshal.AllocHGlobal(Marshal.SizeOf<SdlMessageBoxColorScheme>());
3078  Marshal.StructureToPtr(messageboxdata.colorScheme.Value, colorSchemePtr, false);
3079  }
3080 
3081  int result = INTERNAL_SDL_ShowMessageBox(ref data, out buttonid);
3082 
3083  for (int i = 0; i < messageboxdata.numbuttons; i++)
3084  {
3085  SDL_free(buttons[i].text);
3086  }
3087 
3088  SDL_free(data.message);
3089  SDL_free(data.title);
3090 
3091  if (colorSchemePtr != IntPtr.Zero)
3092  {
3093  Marshal.DestroyStructure<SdlMessageBoxColorScheme>(colorSchemePtr);
3094  Marshal.FreeHGlobal(colorSchemePtr);
3095  }
3096 
3097  return result;
3098  }
3099  finally
3100  {
3101  if (buttonsPtr != IntPtr.Zero)
3102  {
3103  Marshal.FreeHGlobal(buttonsPtr);
3104  }
3105  }
3106  }

6322  public static uint SDL_DEFINE_PIXELFOURCC(byte a, byte b, byte c, byte d) => SDL_FOURCC(a, b, c, d);
6323 
6333  public static uint SDL_DEFINE_PIXELFORMAT(
6334  SdlPixelType type,
6335  uint order,
6336  SdlPackedLayout layout,
6337  byte bits,
6338  byte bytes
6339  )
6340  => (uint) (
6341  (1 << 28) |
6342  ((byte) type << 24) |
6343  ((byte) order << 20) |
6344  ((byte) layout << 16) |
6345  (bits << 8) |
6346  bytes
6347  );
6348 
6354  public static byte SDL_PIXELFLAG(uint x) => (byte) ((x >> 28) & 0x0F);
6355 
6361  public static byte SDL_PIXELTYPE(uint x) => (byte) ((x >> 24) & 0x0F);
6362 
6368  public static byte SDL_PIXELORDER(uint x) => (byte) ((x >> 20) & 0x0F);
6369 
6375  public static byte SDL_PIXELLAYOUT(uint x) => (byte) ((x >> 16) & 0x0F);
6376 
6382  public static byte SDL_BITSPERPIXEL(uint x) => (byte) ((x >> 8) & 0xFF);
6383 
6389  public static byte SDL_BYTESPERPIXEL(uint x)
6390  {
6391  if (SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_FOURCC(x))
6392  {
6393  if (x == SdlPixelformatYuy2 ||
6394  x == SdlPixelformatUyvy ||
6395  x == SdlPixelformatYvyu)
6396  {
6397  return 2;
6398  }
6399 
6400  return 1;
6401  }
6402 
6403  return (byte) (x & 0xFF);
6404  }
6405 
6411  public static bool SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_INDEXED(uint format)
6412  {
6413  if (SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_FOURCC(format))
6414  {
6415  return false;
6416  }
6417 
6418  SdlPixelType pType =
6419  (SdlPixelType) SDL_PIXELTYPE(format);
6420  return pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeIndex1 ||
6421  pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeIndex4 ||
6422  pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeIndex8;
6423  }
6424 
6430  public static bool SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_PACKED(uint format)
6431  {
6432  if (SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_FOURCC(format))
6433  {
6434  return false;
6435  }
6436 
6437  SdlPixelType pType =
6438  (SdlPixelType) SDL_PIXELTYPE(format);
6439  return pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypePacked8 ||
6440  pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypePacked16 ||
6441  pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypePacked32;
6442  }
6443 
6449  public static bool SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_ARRAY(uint format)
6450  {
6451  if (SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_FOURCC(format))
6452  {
6453  return false;
6454  }
6455 
6456  SdlPixelType pType =
6457  (SdlPixelType) SDL_PIXELTYPE(format);
6458  return pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeArrayu8 ||
6459  pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeArrayu16 ||
6460  pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeArrayu32 ||
6461  pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeArrayf16 ||
6462  pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeArrayf32;
6463  }
6464 
6470  public static bool SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_ALPHA(uint format)
6471  {
6472  if (SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_PACKED(format))
6473  {
6474  SdlPackedOrder pOrder =
6475  (SdlPackedOrder) SDL_PIXELORDER(format);
6476  return pOrder == SdlPackedOrder.SdlPackedorderArgb ||
6477  pOrder == SdlPackedOrder.SdlPackedorderRgba ||
6478  pOrder == SdlPackedOrder.SdlPackedorderAbgr ||
6479  pOrder == SdlPackedOrder.SdlPackedorderBgra;
6480  }
6481 
6482  if (SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_ARRAY(format))
6483  {
6484  SdlArrayOrder aOrder =
6485  (SdlArrayOrder) SDL_PIXELORDER(format);
6486  return aOrder == SdlArrayOrder.SdlArrayorderArgb ||
6487  aOrder == SdlArrayOrder.SdlArrayorderRgba ||
6488  aOrder == SdlArrayOrder.SdlArrayorderAbgr ||
6489  aOrder == SdlArrayOrder.SdlArrayorderBgra;
6490  }
6491 
6492  return false;
6493  }

7728  [DllImport(NativeLibName, CallingConvention = CallingConvention.Cdecl)]
7729  private static extern SdlBool SDL_GetEventFilter(
7730  out IntPtr filter,
7731  out IntPtr userdata
7732  );
7733 
7740  public static SdlBool SDL_GetEventFilter(
7741  out SdlEventFilter filter,
7742  out IntPtr userdata
7743  )
7744  {
7745  IntPtr result = IntPtr.Zero;
7746  SdlBool retval = SDL_GetEventFilter(out result, out userdata);
7747  if (result != IntPtr.Zero)
7748  {
7749  filter = (SdlEventFilter) Marshal.GetDelegateForFunctionPointer(
7750  result,
7751  typeof(SdlEventFilter)
7752  );
7753  }
7754  else
7755  {
7756  filter = null;
7757  }
7758 
7759  return retval;
7760  }

9206  [DllImport(NativeLibName, EntryPoint = "SDL_GameControllerGetBindForAxis", CallingConvention = CallingConvention.Cdecl)]

9208  IntPtr gamecontroller,
9209  SdlGameControllerAxis axis
9210  );
9211 
9218  public static SdlGameControllerButtonBind SDL_GameControllerGetBindForAxis(
9219  IntPtr gamecontroller,
9220  SdlGameControllerAxis axis
9221  )
9222  {
9223  // This is guaranteed to never be null
9224  InternalSdlGameControllerButtonBind dumb = INTERNAL_SDL_GameControllerGetBindForAxis(
9225  gamecontroller,
9226  axis
9227  );
9228  SdlGameControllerButtonBind result = new SdlGameControllerButtonBind();
9229  result.bindType = (SdlGameControllerBindType) dumb.bindType;
9230  result.value.hat.hat = dumb.unionVal0;
9231  result.value.hat.hat_mask = dumb.unionVal1;
9232  return result;
9233  }

11195  private static extern int INTERNAL_SDL_OpenURL(byte[] url);

11208  }
